en: Welcome to my realm. How do you like it here?
Really? Well I guess lack of zombies might be shocking for the folks like you.
I think so too, though in the beginning it was hard to get used to.
In a world I claimed as my own.
Why did you take me here?
My name is Sharik. I am a cat.
A destroyed residence of a goddess. A distorted home. Here it is better not to rely on your eyes too much. They will deceive you.
Because you wanted to see "something". Isn't THIS quite something?
I am glad, I did not misjudge you. Say, do you want to spend some coin?
Because I don't want to starve to death, thank you very much.
I don't want to spend money.
Terrific,because I have a few items to sell. Here take a look.
Then I guess we have nothing more to talk about.
